{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.520", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Pr\u00e4sidentin! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.200", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.440", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich freue mich sehr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.160", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir an dieser Stelle\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.560", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich glaube, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.640", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es ist sogar erstmalig so\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.440", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00fcber die Situation in der Krankenpflege und in der Altenpflege reden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.920", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und zwar mit dem eindeutigen Willen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.840", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der von allen Beteiligten hier im Parlament vertreten und ge\u00e4u\u00dfert wurde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.200", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sofort etwas zu tun."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.960", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist etwas, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.000", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weswegen ich sagen w\u00fcrde\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.880", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch an die W\u00e4hlerinnen und W\u00e4hler\u00a0\u2013: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.520", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u201eW\u00e4hlen lohnt\u201c; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.680", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn es zeigt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.160", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Druck gemacht worden ist \u00fcber die Gewerkschaften und die vielen Initiativen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.840", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zum Beispiel \u201ePflege am Boden\u201c und andere\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.680", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die deutlich gemacht haben: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.560", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist h\u00f6chste Zeit."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.400", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das muss man tats\u00e4chlich auch den Vertreterinnen und Vertretern der Gro\u00dfen Koalition nach vier Jahren vorwerfen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.040", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben zwar wirklich viel bewegt\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.120", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben viele Pflegest\u00e4rkungsgesetze und eine umfangreiche Krankenhausreform auf den Weg gebracht\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "83.280", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber die Situation der Arbeitskr\u00e4fte in der Pflege hat sich nicht wirklich entscheidend ge\u00e4ndert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "83.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "85.720", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das muss man n\u00fcchtern feststellen,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "85.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.400", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und man muss wirklich sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.400", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hier haben wir Handlungsbedarf. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.400", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Genau das zeigt sich deutlicher denn je."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.920", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben jetzt zwei Antr\u00e4ge vorliegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.240", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die auf der einen Seite auf das Problem hinweisen und auf der anderen Seite bestimmte L\u00f6sungen aufzeigen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.920", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir werden uns wahrscheinlich nicht \u00fcber alle Fraktionen hinweg auf alle diese L\u00f6sungsinstrumente verst\u00e4ndigen k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.080", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber es deutet sich doch an, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.520", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir ein Sofortprogramm in der Altenpflege und in der Krankenpflege brauchen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.680", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und zwar beides mit einem gro\u00dfen Umfang. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "130.920", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In der Krankenpflege muss es um 25\u00a0000 neue Arbeitspl\u00e4tze gehen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "130.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "135.000", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es muss in der Altenpflege um eine richtig gro\u00dfe Anzahl Fachkr\u00e4fte gehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "135.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "142.640", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die auch wirklich in der praktischen Arbeit dort ankommen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "142.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.280", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das muss sicher, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.200", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "stabil und verl\u00e4sslich finanziert werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.680", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damit wir sicher sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.040", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es zu dieser Entlastung kommt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.120", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn wir das erreicht haben und gleichzeitig einsehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "157.920", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass diese Sofortprogramme nur ein Vorgriff sein k\u00f6nnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "157.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "159.680", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil sie nicht regelhaft sind\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "159.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.080", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir brauchen ja eine nachhaltige L\u00f6sung\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "163.840", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann sehen wir ebenfalls: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "163.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "171.680", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir brauchen erg\u00e4nzend verbindliche Personalbemessungssysteme im Krankenhaus und in der Altenpflege."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "171.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.960", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da reichen die Untergrenzen in pflegesensiblen Bereichen im Krankenhaus nicht aus."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "180.280", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es reicht auch nicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "180.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.320", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "f\u00fcr die Altenpflege zu sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "186.960", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir werden das erst einmal entwickeln, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "186.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "188.080", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und dann m\u00fcssen wir sehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "188.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "190.520", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob wir das bundesweit durchsetzen k\u00f6nnen.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "190.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.080", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.000", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir brauchen ein klares Signal und die klare Bereitschaft vonseiten der Politik: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "201.800", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sorgen durch normative gesetzliche Rahmenbedingungen daf\u00fcr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "201.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "205.200", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Arbeitsbedingungen in der Pflege stimmen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "205.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.920", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das sind wir den Pflegekr\u00e4ften schuldig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.920", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die zwar jetzt noch motiviert sind und in der Regel der Meinung sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "217.120", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sie einen sinnstiftenden Beruf haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "217.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "226.120", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und trotzdem diesen Beruf in der Krankenpflege im Schnitt nach 13\u00a0Jahren und in der Altenpflege nach 8\u00a0Jahren verlassen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "226.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.600", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil sie sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "230.040", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich kann diesen Beruf nicht weiter aus\u00fcben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "230.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "231.680", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "obwohl ich ihn liebe.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "231.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.520", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das muss uns zu denken geben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "236.600", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das muss f\u00fcr uns ein Warnzeichen sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "236.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "238.360", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "endlich und auch schnell zu handeln; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "238.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "243.320", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn wir k\u00f6nnen uns diesen Notstand aus verschiedenen Gr\u00fcnden nicht leisten,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "243.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.000", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "n\u00e4mlich aus Gr\u00fcnden der Patientensicherheit und der Pflegequalit\u00e4t und auch deshalb, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.800", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil wir, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "253.160", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie wir wissen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "253.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "254.560", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht weniger, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "254.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "257.320", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern mehr Fachkr\u00e4fte brauchen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "257.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "262.600", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir werden noch viel mehr Fachkr\u00e4fte f\u00fcr diesen Zukunftsberuf gewinnen m\u00fcssen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "262.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "265.280", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daf\u00fcr brauchen wir attraktive, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "265.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "268.720", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "familienfreundliche Bedingungen und nat\u00fcrlich\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "268.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "270.160", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gerade in der Altenpflege\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "270.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "271.160", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "eine Bezahlung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "271.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "272.200", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die stimmt und dem, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "272.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "274.840", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was dort an Leistung erbracht wird, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "274.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "276.800", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ann\u00e4hernd gerecht wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "276.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "280.560", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Davon sind wir heute gerade in der Altenpflege noch weit entfernt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "280.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "281.880", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da muss sich etwas tun."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "281.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "283.760", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dazu geh\u00f6rt auch\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "283.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "285.800", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das richte ich an die FDP\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "285.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "290.760", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir uns f\u00fcr einen allgemeinverbindlichen \u201eTarifvertrag Soziales\u201c starkmachen,\u00a0\u2013"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "290.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "292.920", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das machen wir aber dann in der n\u00e4chsten Debatte."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "292.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "294.000", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u2013\u00a0der dazu f\u00fchrt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "294.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "295.840", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir auch versprechen k\u00f6nnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
